metadata.name: Hawk
metadata.description:
[D-Mention]  
D-Mention is a coined word composed of Dimension + Mention, based on the concept of pursuing and producing creative work that is not bound by dimensions or preconceptions.

Winner of the Excellence Award in the Design Category of Adobe's "Year-End Creative Contest"

[D-Mention]  
次元や先入観に囚われないクリエイティブの追求と制作というコンセプトを元に、Dimension+Mentionで構成された造語です。

Adobe主催「年末クリエイティブコンテスト」デザイン部門 優秀賞 受賞作品
